        <p>Let the enamel-safe formula lift stains for 30 minutes.</p>
        <span class="step-meta">⏳ 30 minutes</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-icon-ring"><span class="step-emoji">✨</span><span class="step-number">3</span></div>
        <h3>Reveal</h3>
        <p>Peel off, rinse, and reveal a visibly brighter smile.</p>
        <span class="step-meta">🪞 Instant glow</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

